                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ying.neverland/">文郢</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">文字不艰深，囿于时间，否则可以细细读读，应该还蛮有趣</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="462944269">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-462944269" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-462944269" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="462944269">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Horace.Wang/">小盐</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-12-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">又读完刚主一书。附录部分只能南回之后再看。刚主此书早就买了，但是那时候就如读不进陈寅恪的书一样，现在忽然都能读进去了，是不是心境发生了大变化？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

